Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:39.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, this way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.67,0:01:41.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's near! Beyond this forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:45.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We were in search of\NSacred Jewel fragments...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:47.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}when we met up unexpectedly\nwith Kohaku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:49.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}who was being attacked by\NNaraku's demon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:55.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The demon was after the Sacred\NJewel fragment in Kohaku's back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.83,0:02:04.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:08.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango was overjoyed at\nthis reunion with Kohaku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.04,0:02:11.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Kohaku's memory had been\nerased by Naraku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:13.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and remembered nothing\nabout Sango.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.14,0:02:19.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku has come back to me.\NHe's escaped from Naraku's grasp...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.02,0:02:23.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what I want to believe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:27.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,About Kohaku... It's Naraku's trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.42,0:02:29.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I believe in Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:30.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's Naraku's aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:34.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What else can I do except\nto trust him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.26,0:02:39.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just then, Kagura appeared\nto take back the fragment...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:42.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}bringing an army\nof demons with her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:45.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the Sacred Jewel fragment is\nremoved from his back, Kohaku will die!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.34,0:02:48.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}In order to protect Kohaku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:50.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha and Miroku began\nfighting them off...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:54.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}while Kohaku and I escaped\ninto the forest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.12,0:03:04.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to remember...\nabout her and everything else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.63,0:03:08.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...what's this feeling?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:12.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel scared... Something I don't\nwant to remember...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.47,0:03:13.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.24,0:03:16.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kill her... Kill Kagome.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:22.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're all out of arrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:32.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:43.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:58.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't worry, Kohaku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:02.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll never let Naraku\ntake you away ever again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:07.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:10.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:32.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:35.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We must distract Kagura and\nher demons as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:36.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:41.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura! You need a whole army\njust to capture one kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:42.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fine with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:46.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're falling for Naraku's plan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:50.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do your work, Kohaku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:53.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What perfect timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.07,0:04:57.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,While we're at it,\nwe'll slaughter you all, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.41,0:05:01.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha... your head is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:04.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dance of Blades!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:27.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:33.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.28,0:05:36.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}All of a sudden, he's changed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:48.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku, kill Kagome.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:51.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kill her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:11.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kill!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:15.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.65,0:06:20.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kill! Kill!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:23.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kill!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:27.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:33.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome! Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:36.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:39.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:42.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you are still...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:50.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:56.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm all right. It's not serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:06:59.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:01.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara, stay with Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.03,0:07:03.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, it must hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.33,0:07:06.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:13.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:16.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:19.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango's not planning{\i0} to... {\i1}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:24.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no end to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:32.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dance of Blades!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:37.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:40.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why don't you draw your sword,\NInuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:44.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Using the Tetsusaiga to kill the likes\nof you is wasteful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:50.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:56.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you using your claws because you\nstill can't control your sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.09,0:07:58.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're so smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:01.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:03.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.06,0:08:06.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So that's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:10.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up! I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:15.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:21.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:24.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're having an awkward\ntime of it with your sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:28.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn! It's still too heavy\nto wield easily.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.92,0:08:36.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We must keep those demons\nbelieving that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:39.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku is hiding inside the hut.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:06.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:08.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pay attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.46,0:09:46.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So the hut was empty?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:50.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You had us fooled all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:52.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're not going, Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:56.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We still haven't finished this fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:00.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it{\i0} be... {\i1}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.54,0:10:03.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't be tricked, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:05.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.51,0:10:09.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We thought Kohaku was\NKagura and the demons' aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:14.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yet, none of them\nare trying to go after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:17.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe... they faked all this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:20.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and {\i1}we{\i0} were the ones\nwho were tricked!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:26.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If Naraku's true aim\nwas not Kohaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:27.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:30.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's taken Kohaku into the forest!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.61,0:10:34.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So Naraku is still in control of Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.41,0:10:39.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You only realized it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:41.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's probably too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:45.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn you!\NUsing Kohaku to get to Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:46.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:49.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, the one who uses\nthe bow and arrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:50.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:11:00.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku! What're you doing?\NThere are poison insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.44,0:11:02.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:17.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku! Don't be so rash!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:22.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:26.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're sucking in\nthe poison insects, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:33.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, go after Sango and Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:36.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Gotcha! Sorry, Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.14,0:11:40.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you dare die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:42.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- As if I'd let you get away!\N- Don't move, Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:45.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I turn, I'll suck you in, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:48.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:50.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:57.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:06.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:10.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We... must... hurry after Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:13.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.48,0:12:23.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn kid! Looking like\nhe wouldn't even hurt a fly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:26.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:03.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.10,0:13:08.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:12.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you haven't escaped\nfrom Naraku's grasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:17.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You came to hurt Kagome...\nto steal the Sacred Jewel fragments.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:22.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rather than let Naraku continue\nhis control over you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:24.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd rather...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:29.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku, I will free you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:51.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku! I won't let you go alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:58.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will follow immediately.\NSo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:02.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:09.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! Go after Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:10.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She seemed strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.56,0:14:14.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!\NYou've been hurt by Kohaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:16.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's just a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:21.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And that boy, if he really wanted to,\nhad a chance to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:23.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:27.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango doesn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:32.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She may intend to kill Kohaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:35.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:44.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku didn't finish off Kagome.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:48.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does that mean he disobeyed\NNaraku's orders?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.43,0:14:49.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If{\i0} so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.77,0:14:55.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}even if he is being mind-controlled,\NKohaku still has a human heart!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:13.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:20.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uh...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:24.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:26.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is embarrassing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.97,0:15:29.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What're you so shy for?\NWe're siblings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:34.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku, you won't go\nanywhere anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:39.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because you're my brother...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:46.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}because you're my\none and only brother...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.12,0:15:50.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll kill you, then kill myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.89,0:15:55.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the only way to get\nyou back from Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:15:59.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:12.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll kill you, then kill myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:18.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the only way to get\nyou back from Naraku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:21.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forgive me, Kohaku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:32.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop, Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:55.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.92,0:16:57.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't stop me, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.43,0:17:03.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid fool! Killing Kohaku\nwill only please Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.87,0:17:10.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku! Why don't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:13.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,snap out of it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:27.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.12,0:17:33.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As ordered,\NKohaku will kill Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:36.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku is unable to defy Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:38.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:40.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.34,0:17:44.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,why do you think Kohaku\nhas lost his memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:46.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because Naraku\nis controlling his mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.84,0:17:48.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:52.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Kohaku himself\nis resisting remembering...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.12,0:17:56.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,such terrible memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:11.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop! Don't say anything\nmore in front of Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:18.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you... Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:22.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku didn't want to remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:25.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so Naraku granted his wish\nand erased his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:31.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, it's so easy to manipulate\nsomeone with no memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:40.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku! Remember!\NRemember it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:42.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,About Sango and the slayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.90,0:18:46.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:50.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Remembering each and every detail!\NIf you want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:51.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.67,0:18:54.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If he doesn't remember it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:57.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,he'll continue to be under\NNaraku's control...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:19:04.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and Naraku will take the Sacred Jewel\nin his back and kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.09,0:19:11.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You say awful things, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:22.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.94,0:19:25.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If he really remembers\neverything he did...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.91,0:19:28.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,this kid will truly be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:33.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's kindness to let him die\nwithout remembering a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:48.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:55.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.30,0:19:56.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.77,0:20:01.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.28,0:20:06.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the same thing all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:09.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn, what troublesome siblings!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:11.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.09,0:20:13.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:17.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let me tell you this,\nso you don't jump the gun next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:20.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku ordered Kohaku\nto kill Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:24.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Kohaku didn't kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:27.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's because he still\nhas a human heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.64,0:20:33.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why we cannot kill Kohaku.\NGet him alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:35.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:40.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.13,0:20:53.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.83,0:21:00.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I spared your life\nand made you forget everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:04.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yet you failed to kill Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:08.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why is that, Kohaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:15.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you want to\nregain your humanity?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:18.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then do you want to remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.89,0:21:22.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Remember it all?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.33,0:21:26.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.80,0:21:36.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:41.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll let you live for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.04,0:21:43.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forget it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.09,0:21:52.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.93,0:22:08.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...I can't forget\nthat woman's face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.04,0:23:49.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A village is attacked by bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.94,0:23:55.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Gatenmaru, the vicious leader, is\nactually a moth demon in disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.74,0:23:59.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha and Miroku are\ntrapped in a poison cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.41,0:24:03.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Sesshomaru searches for\nclues to how Inuyasha transforms...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.05,0:24:07.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and learns frightening secrets from\na tree demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.66,0:24:12.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Inuyasha's Soul, Devoured"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.09,0:24:14.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
